      "body": "**Release v 0.3.7**\r\n\r\nChanged the way the database files are now named. A single directory called _current_ will contain the \r\n\r\nVMR.xlsx\r\nICTV.msh \r\nBacteriophage_genomes.fasta.gz \r\nM.ap \r\n\r\nThese 4 files form the basis of the database to allow for rapid search of genomes. By putting in a single directory it is easier to update in the future without having to update multiple links \r\n\r\nAs new releases of the MSL appear each year, a directory of previous years will be produced. Allowing multiple databases to easily maintained \r\n\r\nThe current release used is VMR_41v1 released in March 2026 .  All precomputed databases, genomes , *msh and M.pa have been updated to reflect this new taxonomy \r\n"
